{
  "stem": "4513.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, how are you-- how do you, as a black soldier, reconcile the fact and live with the fact that you're discriminated against, you're segregated against, you're-- you're treated badly, and yet you fight?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And yet you have a long record here of fighting 'cause that's the only way you'd be here?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, what's that all about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, only way I can explain this is that I guess I'm fighting for the right to fight when I get back home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Is that one of the things that kept  you going too?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I'm sure it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just kept saying, we gotta end this crazy thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the reason why since the war, I'd been involved with Dr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "King.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think I've been in a jail in every state in the South.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I've been constantly fighting for people's rights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I think I can explain this one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "King and I sat up one night and he asked me the question, why are you here, Paul?' He said, you're here, you're going with us to all these crazy places.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People throwing you in jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "King, I saw a camp once where millions of people had been through and died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, you know something?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know what the end of bigotry looks like-- the solution to bigotry looks like from the standpoint of the bigot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
